title: Bosch Universal Plus Kitchen Machine Comparison
description: This Bosch universal plus kitchen machine features a wide range of optional accessories to eliminate the need for many additional kitchen appliances. This universal kitchen machine features an 800-watt motor, 6.5 quart capacity and an easy-to-clean removable drive shaft.
